1.20	2007_PGA_Championship	2007 PGA Championship	The 2007 PGA Championship was played from August 9 to August 12 at Southern Hills Country Club in Tulsa, Oklahoma. The tournament was won by Tiger Woods, who had previously had little success playing at Southern Hills. It was the fourth PGA Championship at Southern Hills; the three previous winners were Dave Stockton (1970), Raymond Floyd (1982) and Nick Price (1994). Television coverage was provided by TNT and CBS.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b2/PGAChampionship2007Logo.svg/140px-PGAChampionship2007Logo.svg.png
